cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI

This paper deals with the issue of online video piracy, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the analysis of content and the use of indexing services, which could be classified under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper explores the use of streaming cyberlockers, which could be considered a form of distributed systems (cs.DL) and social networks (cs.SI).
